<subSubSection id="8151EE8E055CD67D818E33A48C9BFB00" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="196F7EA621BD4A2D3C782E5FD00DE399" pageNumber="357">
<taxonomicName id="9D630FBC9B877B392ED7BAEDF99F5F24" LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:24819" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Perissomyrmex" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Perissomyrmex Smith" lsidName-HNS="Perissomyrmex Smith" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="357" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Perissomyrmex</taxonomicName>
M. R. Smith 1947: 281. Type-species: 
